properties.name: Moscow in the Summer
properties.description: Posted by MswansonVaz LadaAfter graduating from High School I took a trip with my Russian Language class to Russia to visit Flint\'s sister city Togliatti. We cruised up the Volga to Moscow and St. Petersburg

properties.name: Things to do in Russia on your 18th Birthday
properties.description: Posted by MswansonSt. Petersburg RussiaThe last stop on our trip to Russia was St. Petersburg. We arrived on the evening of my 18th Birthday. Hopped on the Subway and went into downtown. Watched the gates slam shut behind us. I guess we caught the last train. So how\'d I spend my birthday? Walking back to the boat. It was light when we started, only slightly dimmer during the walk, and back to broad daylight by the time we arrived 4 hours later.
